cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.DS 

This paper is about deep neural network ensembles, which are commonly used in machine learning and computer vision tasks. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.CV (Computer Vision) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper proposes a new method for training these ensembles, which involves clustering and transfer learning, which could also fall under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms).
